cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with face recognition through windshields using a custom imaging system and a neural network for HDR fusion. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, specifically neural networks, which could place it in the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM) or machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves fine-tuning the HDR output, which could place it in the sub-category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves hardware development, which could place it in the sub-category of graphics (cs.GR).
